{"tid":2052980,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加碼失業救濟養懶人？ 美眾議員倡改派「復工獎金」","createTime":"2020-06-06T02:29:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T03:33:44.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7362467fe6384a6724085d7076536be2616da30b","tid":2052980,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T02:29:31.000Z","msg":"芝加哥大學經濟學家估計，全美有大約68%失業工人，所獲得「加碼」失業救濟金額，較原來工資為高。白宮開始憂慮，工人失去重返工作崗位的誘因，窒礙商業活動重啟，並拖慢經濟復甦。有國會議員提出，在撥出部份聯邦「救市」基金，作恢復上班的獎金。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200606/AEIBVGX44LRA7YJ7SAKY2RBTKE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200606%2FAEIBVGX44LRA7YJ7SAKY2RBTKE%2F&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGUcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=1528c4c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200606%2FAEIBVGX44LRA7YJ7SAKY2RBTKE%2F&h=cae4a63e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200606/AEIBVGX44LRA7YJ7SAKY2RBTKE/</a>"},{"pid":"13dabc4c3ff4bce1b8b664355ffd2da6d32ccd30","tid":2052980,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T02:30:18.000Z","msg":"仲以為講香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e05043f5681f0a3048ae6e6368be055d1f17d2","tid":2052980,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13dabc4c3ff4bce1b8b664355ffd2da6d32ccd30","tid":2052980,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T02:30:18.000Z","msg":"仲以為講香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T03:31:36.000Z","msg":"你諗多咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03684d4564fdee2ec31ec0b67dec6a3f2a4fecd0","tid":2052980,"uid":77717,"like":1,"dislike":0